item.title: Who am I?
item.description: Hello, I’m Even. I’m the Technical Implementation Manager for DNB. I work with optimizing data collection across the whole organization. This is the place where I will put my writings about projects I work on and general tips and tricks I have picked up during my time here. If you want to reach out to me you can reach me on my email evenanilsen@gmail.com. Here’s my GitHub and my linkedIn.
